OL,3,CTeenager found guilty of sexual
OL,4,Coffences against three schoolgirls
OL,6,FA teenager has been found guilty of
OL,7,Fthe rape of a 13-year-old girl who he
OL,8,Fmet on social media.
OL,10,FSt Peter Port's Ben Frank Spruce, 19,
OL,11,Fwas charged with two counts of rape -
OL,12,Fas well as one count of sexual
OL,13,Fassault, and two counts of sexual
OL,14,Ftouching of a child against two other
OL,15,Fschoolgirls.
OL,17,FAt Guernsey Royal Court today (Tuesday
OL,18,F18 March 2025), Jurats took just two
OL,19,Fhours to find Spruce guilty in what
OL,20,Fthe prosecution called a "cut and dry"
OL,21,Fcase.
