OL,3,CTeenager found guilty of sexual
OL,4,Coffences against three schoolgirls
OL,6,FTwo counts involved the rape of a 13-
OL,7,Fyear-old girl in a field near Castel
OL,8,FHospital on Boxing Day, 2023.
OL,10,FSpruce sent the victim unsolicited
OL,11,Fpictures and pressured her to meet in
OL,12,Fperson.
OL,14,FThe defendant denied messaging or
OL,15,Fmeeting the girl during the trial, but
OL,16,Fafter Spruce's phone was seized in
OL,17,FJanuary in an unrelated search, police
OL,18,Ffound his location history placed him
OL,19,Fclose to the scene on the day.
