OL,6,FThe victim says she still feels scared
OL,7,Fand disgusted, adding she now freezes
OL,8,Fif a boy accidentally touches her.
OL,10,FSpruce was also found guilty of the
OL,11,Fsexual touching of a 14-year-old
OL,12,Faround the lanes at Beau Sejour.
OL,14,FAgain, Spruce used social media to
OL,15,Fpressure the victim to meet in person,
OL,16,Fwith the victim saying that Spruce
OL,17,Ftold her to: "Come or you'll make it
OL,18,Fworse for yourself".
